cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY

The paper deals with the verification and certification of logical properties of neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the sub-fields of machine learning (cs.LG), computer security and cryptography (cs.CR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and control systems (cs.SY). The paper specifically focuses on security applications of the proposed framework, which further supports the likelihood of the paper belonging to these sub-categories.
